{"ts": "2026-06-09T00:36:29.622192+00:00", "update": {"model": {"messages": [{"type": "ai", "data": {"content": "Unfortunately, both file-writing tools returned **403 (Resource not accessible by personal access token)** — the token provided doesn't have write access to this repository. I cannot push the changes directly.\n\n---\n\n## Summary of Proposed Changes\n\nHere's exactly what needs to change to satisfy Issue #3's acceptance criteria:\n\n### 1. `zap/baseline.conf`\n\n**Current content:**\n```\n# OWASP ZAP baseline configuration for local demo app\n# Format: rule_id   action   reason\n10020\tWARN\tMissing anti-clickjacking header is accepted for this local text-only demo.\n```\n\n**Proposed content** (add one line):\n```\n# OWASP ZAP baseline configuration for local demo app\n# Format: rule_id   action   reason\n10020\tWARN\tMissing anti-clickjacking header is accepted for this local text-only demo.\n10038\tFALSE_POSITIVE\tContent-Security-Policy header is not needed for this local text-only demo endpoint that serves no executable content.\n```\n\n**Why rule 10038?** The app (`app.py`) serves only `text/plain` — no HTML, no JavaScript. A Content-Security-Policy header is irrelevant for plain-text responses, making this a well-justified false positive.\n\n### 2. `docs/rule_waivers.md`\n\n**Current content:**\n```\n# Rule Waivers\n\nWaivers must include rule id, action, and local-demo justification.\n```\n\n**Proposed content** (append a table):\n```markdown\n# Rule Waivers\n\nWaivers must include rule id, action, and local-demo justification.\n\n| Rule ID | Action         | Justification |\n|---------|----------------|---------------|\n| 10038   | FALSE_POSITIVE | The local demo endpoint (`http://127.0.0.1:8080/`) returns a plain-text response with no executable content (no HTML, no JavaScript). A Content-Security-Policy header is therefore unnecessary and its absence poses no risk in this context. |\n```\n\n### Validation Check\n\nThe validation script (`scripts/validate_repo.py`) checks that:\n1. Required files exist (`README.md`, `SECURITY.md`, `zap/baseline.conf`, `sample_data/zap_baseline.json`, `scripts/run_zap_baseline.sh`) — ✅ all still present\n2. `scripts/run_zap_baseline.sh` contains `'Refusing non-local target'` — ✅ untouched\n\nThese changes would pass validation without issue.\n\n### Limitation\n\n**The changes could not be committed** because the access token lacks write permission to this repository (`403 Resource not accessible by personal access token`). To apply them, either:\n- Grant the token write access and retry, or\n- Apply the changes manually using the content above.", "additional_kwargs": {"refusal": null}, "response_metadata": {"token_usage": {"completion_tokens": 814, "prompt_tokens": 13382, "total_tokens": 14196, "completion_tokens_details": {"accepted_prediction_tokens": null, "audio_tokens": 0, "reasoning_tokens": 221, "rejected_prediction_tokens": null, "image_tokens": 0}, "prompt_tokens_details": {"audio_tokens": 0, "cached_tokens": 12992, "cache_write_tokens": 0, "video_tokens": 0}, "cost": 0, "is_byok": true, "cost_details": {"upstream_inference_cost": 0.0009246012, "upstream_inference_prompt_cost": 0.0002164212, "upstream_inference_completions_cost": 0.00070818}}, "model_provider": "openai", "model_name": "xiaomi/mimo-v2.5-pro-20260422", "system_fingerprint": null, "id": "gen-1780965364-TOqA8ZLf8ti1oGjwr2NX", "finish_reason": "stop", "logprobs": null}, "type": "ai", "name": null, "id": "lc_run--019ea9ce-d08d-7551-84d4-7a25520f41c3-0", "tool_calls": [], "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 13382, "output_tokens": 814, "total_tokens": 14196, "input_token_details": {"audio": 0, "cache_read": 12992}, "output_token_details": {"audio": 0, "reasoning": 221}}}}]}}}
